      • forceDeleteRepository

        void forceDeleteRepository(String uniqueName,
                         String repositoryKey)
                           throws ServiceException,
                                  CmisObjectNotFoundException
        Deletes the tenant repository of the current tenant used by the current consuming account including all data contained within. This happens even if the repository is not empty and can lead to data loss
        Throws:
        ServiceException
        CmisObjectNotFoundException
        See Also:
        EcmFactory.forceDeleteRepository(String, String)
